  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"iVcNQKSP\">不是。</p><p data-pid=\"R0npAOeL\">简而言之：基因构成完全来源于母体不等于基因和母体完全相同</p><p data-pid=\"iWEadSWK\">假设存在可育双性人，非嵌合体，不考虑突变。</p><p data-pid=\"dWcd5K1S\">其形成生殖细胞时可能分出<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=542569175&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%90%8C%E6%BA%90%E6%9F%93%E8%89%B2%E4%BD%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">同源染色体<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>中的任意一个。母体的每组染色体中来自母体父方和母体母方的两条不一样，那么母体自交所育子代的每组染色体根据自由组合可能存在以下情况：</p><p data-pid=\"JMF0LelA\">母母/母父/父母/父父</p><p data-pid=\"r7_Jvd1K\">父和母分别表示同源染色体的根本来源是子代母体的再上一辈父本和母本</p><p data-pid=\"oQ-HuNk-\">其中母父和父母组合可以认为和原母体相同，每组染色体有1/2的概率和母体相同。</p><p data-pid=\"SyV0nvtL\">一共二十三对，那么完全相同的概率是1/2的23次方。假设忽略突变和性染色体问题。</p><p data-pid=\"uX3DQrvy\">假两性畸形的患者无法自交。两套生殖器都可育的真两性畸形较为罕见。真两性畸形患者大部分染色体味46XX。</p><p data-pid=\"P3-JGHhS\">47xxy<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=542569175&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%85%8B%E6%B0%8F%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E5%BE%81&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">克氏综合征<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的患者部分可以通过试管取精子生育后代，但是没有女性生殖器。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f28968a0fdf8ad3496003179c9831f1e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"344\" data-rawheight=\"182\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-45105802f6fa6d2775e7281e68b93f87\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f463db627c03dfaa7da1c84e8ccc1b6_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"344\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='344' height='182'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"344\" data-rawheight=\"182\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-45105802f6fa6d2775e7281e68b93f87\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6f463db627c03dfaa7da1c84e8ccc1b6_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"344\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f28968a0fdf8ad3496003179c9831f1e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5a5e891543bdc7b055e40377740c06d7_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"554\" data-rawheight=\"504\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-88212574dff63b29e2e87704b9e35c37\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-171546d5a00aa428a37b258f4e7099b6_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"554\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5a5e891543bdc7b055e40377740c06d7_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='554' h